data.description: Welcome to your new HOME! A well-maintained gem that's ready to welcome its new owners! This exquisite home, just 10 years young, boasts a wealth of features that blend comfort, style, and functionality.  As you step through the front door, on this level, you'll find a convenient half bath, perfect for guests, as well as a spacious office with elegant French doors that offer privacy and tranquility. The adjacent rec room/family room combo provides the ideal space for relaxation and entertainment, with ample natural light streaming in. Hardwood floors grace the foyer, kitchen, dining room, and living room areas. The rec room/family room is not only inviting but also practical, featuring a full storage closet for all your organizational needs. Beyond, you'll discover a separate 2-car garage, making parking a breeze. In addition to the garage, you'll have two designated parking spaces right outside the garage door for added convenience. The heart of this home is undoubtedly the kitchen, where gathering dreams come true. Stainless steel appliances, including a brand-new Whirlpool refrigerator. Granite countertops beautifully complement the 42-inch wooden cabinets, providing an abundance of storage space. The kitchen island offers even more cabinetry and is perfect for casual dining or meal preparation.  On the third floor, you'll find a full walk-in laundry room, making laundry day a breeze. The owner's suite is a true retreat, featuring a tray ceiling with a fan/light insert. The owner's suite bathroom boasts double vanity sinks, a relaxing soaking tub, a stand-up shower, and a spacious walk-in closet – a perfect sanctuary to unwind after a long day. The third floor also offers two additional well-appointed bedrooms, each with its own unique charm. The hall bathroom on this level features a tub/shower combo. This home has been lovingly maintained, with freshly painted bathrooms (9/28) and professionally cleaned carpets (10/06), ensuring that it's in pristine condition and ready for its new owners to move right in. Located in close proximity to the Blue Crab Baseball stadium, this home offers the perfect blend of convenience and dining. Don't miss your opportunity to make this your forever home – schedule a showing today and make this dream home a reality!  Seller prefers Cardinal Title Group!  Seller offering a 1-year home warranty!  Home is Home Partners approved (Rent to Own Option)
